{"prompt": "Generate a website for a restaurant chain. The website should be cozy and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Cozy Bites Restaurant</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #4682B4; /* Steel Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #B0C4DE; /* Light Steel Blue */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #F5F5DC; /* Beige */\n            --accent-color: #DAA520; /* Goldenrod */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            text-decoration: none;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            background-color: white;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            font-size: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item h3 {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .menu-item p {\n            font-style: italic;\n            color: #666;\n        }\n\n        .gallery {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 15px;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .gallery img {\n            width: 200px;\n            height: 150px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            border: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info p {\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info a {\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(70, 130, 180, 0.7), rgba(70, 130, 180, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/4682B4/FFFFFF?text=Delicious+Food') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: white;\n            height: 400px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: white;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .reservation-form {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .reservation-form input,\n        .reservation-form textarea,\n        .reservation-form button {\n            width: 80%;\n            max-width: 400px;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .reservation-form button {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: white;\n            border: none;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .reservation-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #e0a000; /* Darker shade of accent */\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Cozy Bites Restaurant</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#menu\">Menu</a>\n        <a href=\"#gallery\">Gallery</a>\n        <a href=\"#reservations\">Reservations</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Warm Atmosphere, Delicious Food</h2>\n        <p>Experience the comfort of home with our exquisite dishes.</p>\n    </section>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Welcome to Cozy Bites</h2>\n            <p>Founded with a passion for creating a welcoming dining experience, Cozy Bites offers a menu inspired by home-style cooking with a touch of elegance. We believe in using fresh, quality ingredients to craft dishes that bring comfort and joy to every guest. Our cozy ambiance is perfect for a relaxed meal with family and friends.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"menu\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Our Signature Menu</h2>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h3>Shepherd's Pie</h3>\n                <p>A hearty blend of savory minced lamb and vegetables, topped with creamy mashed potatoes.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h3>Creamy Tomato Soup</h3>\n                <p>Velvety smooth tomato soup finished with a swirl of cream, served with crusty bread.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h3>Apple Crumble</h3>\n                <p>Warm, baked apples topped with a buttery, crumbly oat topping, served with vanilla ice cream.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"menu-item\">\n                <h3>Grilled Salmon with Lemon Dill Sauce</h3>\n                <p>Fresh salmon fillet grilled to perfection, served with a delicate lemon dill sauce.</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"gallery\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>A Glimpse of Our Kitchen</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200x150/4682B4/FFFFFF?text=Dish+1\" alt=\"Food Image 1\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200x150/B0C4DE/333333?text=Dish+2\" alt=\"Food Image 2\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200x150/DAA520/FFFFFF?text=Dish+3\" alt=\"Food Image 3\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200x150/F5F5DC/333333?text=Dish+4\" alt=\"Food Image 4\">\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"reservations\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Reserve Your Table</h2>\n            <p>Book your cozy dining experience with us!</p>\n            <form class=\"reservation-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <input type=\"date\" required>\n                <input type=\"time\" required>\n                <textarea placeholder=\"Special Requests\" rows=\"3\"></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Book Now</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"section\">\n            <h2>Visit Us</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Cozy Lane, Comfort City, CA 90210</p>\n                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (555) 123-4567</p>\n                <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@cozybites.com</p>\n                <p><strong>Hours:</strong> Mon-Sat: 11:00 AM - 10:00 PM | Sun: 12:00 PM - 9:00 PM</p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Cozy Bites Restaurant. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}